I have submitted an ad proposal. When will it be approved and where can I check the status?

The ad approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. You can check the status of your ad in the Ad Management section of your NewsBreak account. If you have any further questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out!
I have submitted all the information but still asked to submit additional personal documents. What is this?

It seems like your account is undergoing a verification process. To proceed, you might need to provide additional documents for business verification. Please ensure you've submitted the following details:
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once these are provided, our team will review and update you on your account status. If you have any questions, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com.
